snippet: The 2014 Whitney Biennial survey of American art features 103 participants, reflecting some interesting choices, some new faces and three quite different shows under one roof.
abstract: Holland Cotter reviews 2014 Whitney Biennial survey of American art, featuring 103 participants; will be last Biennial before museum moves downtown.
lead_paragraph: The 2014 Whitney Biennial survey of American art features 103 participants, reflecting some interesting choices, some new faces and three quite different shows under one roof.
